{{See also|Internet Explorer Mobile}}

Windows Phone 7.5中內建了一款[[排版引擎|排版引擎]]以[[Internet_Explorer_9|Internet Explorer 9]]做為基礎的[[Internet_Explorer_Mobile|Internet Explorer Mobile]]。在Windows Phone 8中則加入[[Internet_Explorer_10|Internet Explorer 10]] Mobile，具有更多功能，包括對[[HTML5|HTML5]]的加強支援。<ref name="redial">{{Cite web |title=Windows Phone 7.5 Mango in-depth preview |url=http://www.engadget.com/2011/06/27/windows-phone-7-5-mango-in-depth-preview-video/ |accessdate=2010-02-19 |date=2010-02-15 |publisher=Engadget |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629095621/http://www.engadget.com/2011/06/27/windows-phone-7-5-mango-in-depth-preview-video/ |archive-date=2011-06-29 }}</ref>Windows Phone內建的Internet Explorer Mobile 9及10均不支援[[Flash|Flash]]以及[[Silverlight|Silverlight]]。

Windows Phone上的Internet Explorer讓使用者能夠建立一個屬於自己的「我的最愛」清單，並能夠將常用的網頁連結作為動態磚釘選在開始畫面中。該瀏覽器最多支援6個索引標籤，而每個索引標籤中的網頁都能夠個別平行載入。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Exclusive: Windows Phone 7 Web Browser Comparison (Video)<!-- Bot generated title --> |url=http://pocketnow.com/windows-phone/exclusive-windows-phone-7-web-browser-comparison |dead-url=yes |access-date=2011-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111126190449/http://pocketnow.com/windows-phone/exclusive-windows-phone-7-web-browser-comparison |archive-date=2011-11-26 }}</ref>其它的功能包括了多點觸控手勢的支援、精簡的使用者介面、順暢的放大／縮小動畫、可儲存網頁中的圖片、透過電子郵件分享網頁以及網頁的內部搜尋（即搜尋網頁中的文字內容）。<ref>{{Cite web |title=First Look: Internet Explorer on Windows Phone 7 Series |url=http://pocketnow.com/software-1/first-look-internet-explorer-on-windows-phone-7-series |accessdate=2010-09-19 |date=2010-03-15 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110101150935/http://pocketnow.com/software-1/first-look-internet-explorer-on-windows-phone-7-series |archive-date=2011-01-01 }}</ref>微軟宣布將會定期提供Windows Phone網頁瀏覽器及其排版引擎的更新，並會將此更新從Windows Phone的更新系統中獨立出來。<ref>{{Cite web |title=IE Mobile Updates, Program Manager for IE Mobile team comments on update system for the browser |url=http://www.mobiletechworld.com/2010/05/20/the-windows-phone-7-ie-mobile-browser-upgradable-without-a-firmware-update/ |date=2010-05-20 |dead-url=yes |access-date=2011-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111026193905/http://www.mobiletechworld.com/2010/05/20/the-windows-phone-7-ie-mobile-browser-upgradable-without-a-firmware-update/ |archive-date=2011-10-26 }}</ref>

